<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1498,1924]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,303,1498,1524]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Description.</emphasis>
Body length: ɗ, 
<quantity box="[503,589,1498,1524]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" unit="mm" value="6.5">6.5mm</quantity>
. Body colour generally dark brown; vertex with blackish brown apically (
<figureCitation box="[159,228,1538,1564]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<number box="[217,228,1538,1564]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
A); face pale yellow, anteclypeus with pair of stout brown setae apically (
<figureCitation box="[1120,1189,1538,1564]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<number box="[1177,1189,1538,1564]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
B). Head and thorax with somewhat dense pale short setae. Scutellum with some short tufts of black setae laterally (
<figureCitation box="[1266,1332,1578,1604]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<number box="[1321,1332,1578,1604]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
A).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1498,1924]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Male pygofer with distal margin broadly rounded in lateral view (
<figureCitation box="[1019,1090,1618,1644]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<number box="[1079,1090,1618,1644]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
D); subgenital plate slightly extending beyond apex of pygofer side, apex acute in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[962,1034,1658,1684]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Figs 
<number box="[1023,1034,1658,1684]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
D, G). Aedeagal shaft with dense tubercles laterally, apex strongly narrowed distally in ventral view (
<figureCitation box="[958,1030,1698,1724]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Figs 
<number box="[1019,1030,1698,1724]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
C, F, L). Xth segment moderately long (
<figureCitation box="[219,286,1738,1764]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="14.[151,255,1718,1742]" captionTargetBox="[200,1387,311,1657]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[167,1413,277,1692]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 1. Cyrta hirsuta A, head and thorax, dorsal view; B, face; C, connective and aedeagus, lateral view; D, male genital capsule, lateral view; E, style and connective, dorsal view; F, apex of aedeagus, ventral view; G, valve and style, ventral view; H, base of aedeagus and dorsal connective, anteroventral view; I, male genital capsule, dorsal view; J, aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182577/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<date box="[274,286,1738,1764]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<number box="[274,286,1738,1764]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1.0">1</number>
</date>
</figureCitation>
I).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
