<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1498,1924]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,318,1818,1844]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was originally recorded from three specimens (
<typeStatus box="[1053,1159,1818,1844]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">syntypes</typeStatus>
) in the following way: ‘West-China: Sze’-Chuan, Ta-tsien-lu, 
<date box="[623,715,1858,1884]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="1993-06-02">
<number box="[623,639,1858,1884]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="2.0">2</number>
.VI.93
</date>
, 3ɗ von POTANIN gesammelt.’. The male genitalia of this species are figured here for the first time.
</paragraph>
